{{GeoGroupTemplate}} This is a list of the most [[topographic isolation|topographically isolated]] [[mountain]]s of [[Switzerland]]. This list only includes summits with an isolation of at least {{convert|10.0|km|mi|}}, regardless of their [[elevation]] or [[topographical prominence]] (drop). For a general list of mountains, with height and prominence ranking, see [[List of mountains of Switzerland]].
The list includes all eight [[ultra-prominent peak]]s of Switzerland as well as several [[List of Swiss cantons by elevation|canton high points]].
