The '''O.E. Meinzer Award''' is the annual award of the [[Hydrogeology]] Division of the [[Geological Society of America]]. Established in 1965, t is named after [[Oscar Edward Meinzer]] who has been called the "father of modern groundwater hydrology".<ref>{{cite journal|last=Meyer|first=Gerald|title=Oscar E. Meinzer — father of modern groundwater hydrology in the United States|journal=Hydrogeology Journal|date=17 November 2012|volume=3|issue=2|pages=76–78|doi=10.1007/s10040-995-0005-0}}</ref> The Meinzer award recognizes the author or authors of a publication or body of publications that have significantly advanced the science of hydrogeology or a closely related field.<ref>{{cite web|title=O. E. Meinzer Award|url=http://gsahydrogeology.org/OEMeinzer.htm|publisher=Geological Society of America|accessdate=18 September 2015}}</ref>
==List of Recipients== The recipients of the award are:<ref>{{cite web|title=Past O. E. Meinzer Recipients|url=http://community.geosociety.org/hydrodivision/awards/meinzer/past|publisher=Geological Society of America|accessdate=18 September 2015}}</ref> *1965 Tóth, József *1966 McGuinness, C. L. *1967 Stallman, Robert W. *1968 [[Mahdi S. Hantush|Hantush, Mahdi S.]] *1969 Cooper, Hilton H., Jr. *1970 Stringfield, Victor T. *1971 Maxey, George B. *1972 Poland, Joseph F. and Davis, George H. *1973 Back, William and Hanshaw, Bruce B. *1974 Freeze, R. Allan *1975 Bredehoeft, John D. and Pinder, George F. *1976 Neuman, Shlomo P. and Witherspoon, Paul A. *1977 Rubin, Jacob and James, Ronald V. *1978 Nelson, William R. *1979 Sharp, John. M., Jr., and Domenico, P. A. *1980 Cooley, Richard. L. *1981 Bennett, Gordon D. *1983 Weeks, Edwin P. *1984 Schwartz, Franklin W. and Smith, Leslie. J. *1985 Cherry, John A. *1986 Narasimhan, T. N. *1987 Gelhar, Lynn W. *1988 Winograd, Isaac J. *1989 Davis, Stanley N. *1990 Hem, John D. *1991 Neuzil, Christopher E. *1992 Bethke, Craig M. *1993 Plummer, L. Niel *1994 Gorelick, Steven M. *1995 Garven, Grant *1996 Wilson, John L. *1997 Konikow, Leonard F. *1998 Anderson, Mary P. *1999 Sudicky, Edward A. *2000 Chapelle, Francis H. *2001 Philips, Fred M. *2002 Winter, Thomas C. *2003 Ingebritsen, Steven E. *2004 de Marsily, Ghislain *2005 Siegel, Donald I. *2006 Pruess, Karsten *2007 Frape, Shaun *2008 Thorstenson, Donald C. *2009 Edmunds, W. Mike *2010 [[Mary Jo Baedecker|Baedecker, Mary Jo]] *2011 Fogg, Graham E. *2012 Parkhurst, David L. *2013 Zheng, Chunmiao *2014 Harvey, Charles F. *2015 Berkowitz, Brian
